text:
There are a lot of great accounts on X I believe provide great and timely information. 

Including the AI trade, value investing, finding hidden players, etc. 

Here are the accounts I suggest you should follow if you haven't already to improve your knowledge and get all around information:

@BryzonX - semis, AI
@TheBigBerbowski - DC infra, memory, semis, AI
@damnang2 - semi engineer; high detailed analysis
@PhotonCap - photonics & semis research
@PhotonBull - photonics, AI, defense, space
@LIWEI_TWCapital - taiwan semi research
@lithos_graphein - semi news
@jasonschips - semis and optics
@semivision_tw - supply chain, semis, AI, optics
@Aktiehedonist - AI trade
@holden_commodor - finds under the radar plays
@ParadisLabs - jack of all trades 
@ariaradnia - high detailed videos on youtube on SaaS
@ren_stocks - AI trade
@HatedMoats - finds MOAT businesses
@Leoskie_L - taiwan semi research
@Temple_Eight - AI trade
@VantixResearch - highly detailed deep dives 
@rosyprosperity - hidden value companies
@MoodyWriter13 - high research driven investor
@athuinvests - tech & AI
@Monolith_Cap - niche stocks finder
@vikramskr - engineering driven analysis
@Midnight_Captl - AI trade
@TheValueist - great summaries of companies
@latent_value7 - research on AI companies
@mkfilko - technical analysis and AI
@ThematicTrader - deep research
@Aaronwei3n - semi research analyst
@crux_capital_ - photonics & physical AI
@insane_analyst - engineering analysis and free substack

All of them provide valuable insights.

